            <th style="padding: 8px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Fichier</th>
            <th style="padding: 8px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Complexit√©</th>
            <th style="padding: 8px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Lignes</th>
            <th style="padding: 8px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">R√©pertoire</th>
